Introducing OneBrowserSearch: a search extension designed for simplicity and efficiency.
With OneBrowserSearch, Search results are powered by Microsoft Bing.
By simply clicking "Add to Chrome," you consent to the installation of the OneBrowserSearch extension default search, and acknowledgment of our Terms of Use and Privacy Policy.
